<h1 id="-find-criteria-callback-">.find(<code>criteria</code> , [<code>callback</code>])</h1>
<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>Finds and returns all records that meet the criteria object(s) that you pass it.</p>
<h3 id="overview" permalink="overview">Overview</h3>
